<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/27905652">如何评价「买书不看，却又以买书为乐」这种行为？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3345078" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">浮躁起来完全看不进书，但是又很喜欢逛书店逛亚马逊看新书推荐、往家里搬新书，这是病么？</div>


</div>
